{"tid":1223272,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"如果音樂還有能力，希望她能提醒大家不要絕望，輕言放棄。","createTime":"2019-06-14T16:06:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T16:54:59.000Z","uid":10289,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"70af381e89b90c456706ee4a00608cadc27bff20","tid":1223272,"uid":10289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T16:06:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aT6s5RjN73o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaT6s5RjN73o&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8C3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=28587338\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aT6s5RjN73o</a><br />\n呢幾年香港都發生好多事，有樂隊一直以音樂勉勵香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家都可以睇到佢地嘅努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n節錄自description box：<br />\n「用力刮你一巴掌，你會又憤怒又焦急，很想還手，很想怒吼，很想控訴。<br />\n<br />\n但當我每天都用力刮你一巴掌，不知從哪一天開始，你就已經練就成不痛不癢了。<br />\n又記不起自哪一朝開始，越發荒謬的新聞如海嘯傾覆城市，我們選擇逃避，選擇麻木，選擇忘記⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n如果音樂還有能力，希望她能提醒大家不要絕望，輕言放棄。<br />\n<br />\n『活著，留低希冀好嗎？』」"},{"pid":"7d3b31ba381330de1ed63198f3e6fa8810c4f35d","tid":1223272,"uid":5422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T16:54:59.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}